Title: 043: Solving an Optimization Problem with a Custom Built Algorithm
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with AI Researcher Deblina Bhattacharjee. You will be able to discover about the great research opportunities around the world, learn about building an automated healthcare solution and hear how to apply the Fibonacci sequence to solve optimization problems.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/43
